verbose_text: Inhibition of membrane permeabilizing RCD, the promotion of membrane integral cell death, the promotion of barrier integrity or epithelial cell autonomous defenses, and many other host factors should be considered for investigation in designing host directed therapeutic approaches leveraging cell death.
